"class=\"extension\">.desktop</filename> file created in your <filename class="
"\"directory\">Autostart</filename> folder and will be run during Plasma "
"startup."
msgstr ""
"Skriptid ja töölauafailid, mis on määratud käivituma <guilabel>käivitamisel</"
